  <metadata>
    <name>Tour3d 01, Day 1: Schwarzwaldhochstraße to Triberg</name>
    <desc>Ride the full B500 from Baden-Baden to Freudenstadt, then south through Alpirsbach and Schiltach to Triberg.</desc>
